Package gameobjects.nonstaticobjects.monsters

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Clotty
    A Clotty is a Monster that shoot projectile from a distance in all 4 cardinal direction.
    DoubleRedFly
    A double red fly is a FlyingMonster that upon being defeated creates two smaller double red fly.
    Fly
    A fly is a FlyingMonster that can shoot projectile from a distance.
    FlyingMonster
    A FlyingMonster is a Monsters, it's mainly used because of it's unique ability to fly above things that are on the ground.
    FlyingSummoningMonster
    A SummoningMonster is a flying monster that has the special ability of being able to spawn new monsters with the abstract SummoningMonster.updateSummoningGameObject() method.
    Monster
    A Monster is a NonStaticObject, it uses different variables such as, a integer variable attackSpeed, that represents the speed the Monster will be able to damage the hero.
    RedFly
    A red fly is a FlyingMonster that can shoot projectile from a distance.
    Spider
    A Spider is a Monster, which as a unique way of moving, using a random direction, length and moving cooldown.
    SummoningMonster
    A SummoningMonster is a monster that has the special ability of being able to spawn new monsters with the abstract SummoningMonster.updateSummoningGameObject() method.
    Vis
    A Vis is a Monster that can only attack on hand to hand.
